  <para style="mt1">MARŨA KŨRĨ AHIBIRANIA</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Andũ a ndini mĩthemba mĩingĩ, Ayahudi o ũndũ ũmwe na andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ, nĩ maarĩ na ciũria nyingĩ ciakoniĩ Ũkristiano. Nĩmethaga ũira wa kuonania atĩ wĩtĩkio ũyũ mwerũ warĩ wa ma. Ayahudi nĩ maarĩ na ũira wa maũndũ marĩa Ngai aamekĩire ta kũringa Iria Itune, na Kĩrĩkanĩro kĩa Ngai nao Kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩa Sinai. Ningĩ nĩ maarĩ na mũhooere warĩ mũthaka, o na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa wamarutagĩra magongona hekarũ-inĩ nĩguo andũ marekerwo mehia.</para>
  <para style="ip">No Akristiano nĩ kĩĩ maarĩ nakĩo? Wĩtĩkio ũyũ mwerũ ũngĩahotire kũhonokania atĩa, na ũtũme mũndũ agĩe ũrata na Ngai?</para>
  <para style="ip">Marũa kũrĩ Ahibirania maandĩkirwo nĩguo magerie gũcookia ciũria cia mũthemba ũcio. Marũa-inĩ maya mwandĩki nĩerĩte athomi ũrĩa Jesũ arĩ wa bata gũkĩra Musa. We nĩ mũnene gũkĩra araika a Ngai. Jesũ Kristũ nĩwe mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mwagĩrĩru tondũ we ndaigana kwĩhia, ningĩ nĩerutire muoyo wake naguo ũgĩtuĩka igongona rĩagĩrĩru riita rĩmwe rĩa kũigana nĩ ũndũ wa mehia (9:23–10:18). Mwandĩki nĩonanĩtie atĩ Kristũ nĩwe njĩra ĩrĩa njagĩrĩru ya ũguũrio wa Ngai.</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Mwandĩki wa Ibuku rĩĩrĩ ndoĩkaine wega nũũ.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Ũnene wa Kristũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 1:1-3:19">1:1–3:19</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mũtũũrĩre mwega wa mũndũ mwĩtĩkia <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 4:1-16">4:1-16</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Wĩra mũnene wa mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 5:1-8:13">5:1–8:13</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩega makĩria <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 9:1-10:39">9:1–10:39</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Etĩkia njamba a tene <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 11:1-40">11:1-40</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Maũndũ marĩa etĩkia mabataire gwĩka <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 12:1-13:19">12:1–13:19</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ciugo cia kũrĩkĩrĩria <char style="ior"><ref loc="HEB 13:20-25">13:20-25</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũriũ nĩ Mũnene Gũkĩra Araika</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 1:70">Luk 1:70</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 12:6">Ndar 12:6</ref>, <ref loc="NUM 12:8">8</ref></char>
    </note>Matukũ-inĩ ma tene Ngai nĩarĩirie maithe maitũ na tũnua twa anabii maita maingĩ, na njĩra mwanya mwanya, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 1:20">1Pet 1:20</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 2:8">Thab 2:8</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 11:3">Ahib 11:3</ref></char></note>no matukũ-inĩ maya ma kũrigĩrĩria-rĩ, ithuĩ nĩatwarĩirie na njĩra ya Mũriũ, ũrĩa aatuire mũgai wa indo ciothe, o we ũrĩa thĩ yothe yombirwo na ũndũ wake. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:14">Joh 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:17">Akol 1:17</ref>; <ref loc="TIT 2:14">Tit 2:14</ref></char></note>Mũrũwe-rĩ, nĩwe wonanagia ũkengi wa riiri wake, na nĩwe mũhianĩre mũkinyanĩru kũna wa ũrĩa Ngai atariĩ, ningĩ nĩwe ũnyiitĩrĩire indo ciothe na kiugo gĩake kĩrĩ hinya. Nake aarĩkia gũtheria andũ mehia-rĩ, nĩaikarire thĩ guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ũnene kũu igũrũ. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio agĩtuĩka mũnene gũkĩra araika, o ta ũrĩa rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa aagaĩirwo rĩrĩ inene gũkĩra rĩao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 2:7">Thab 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 7:14">2Sam 7:14</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 17:13">Gũcook 17:13</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, nĩ mũraika ũrĩkũ Ngai arĩ eera atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũmũthĩ nĩndatuĩka Thoguo”?</para>
  <para style="m">O na kana akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Nĩ niĩ ngũtuĩka Ithe,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake atuĩke Mũrũ wakwa”?</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 3:16">Joh 3:16</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 32:43">Gũcook 32:43</ref></char>
    </note>Na ningĩ-rĩ, Ngai aarehe irigithathi rĩake gũkũ thĩ, oigire atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Araika othe a Ngai nĩmamũinamĩrĩre, mamũhooe.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 104:4">Thab 104:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Akĩaria ũhoro wa araika oigire atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Atũmaga araika ake matuĩke huho,</para>
  <para style="q2">nacio ndungata ciake agacitua nĩnĩmbĩ cia mwaki.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 1:33">Luk 1:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No ha ũhoro ũkoniĩ Mũriũ ekuuga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee Ngai, gĩtĩ gĩaku kĩa ũnene nĩgĩgatũũra tene na tene,</para>
  <para style="q2">nakĩo kĩhooto nĩkĩo gĩgaatuĩka mũthĩgi wa ũthamaki waku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 61:1">Isa 61:1</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 61:3">3</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 45:6-7">Thab 45:6-7</ref></char>
    </note>Wee wendete ũthingu no ũgathũũra waganu;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩ ũndũ ũcio, Ngai, o we Ngai waku, nĩakwambararĩtie gũkĩra athiritũ aku othe</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũndũ wa gũgũitĩrĩria maguta ma gĩkeno.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 8:6">Thab 8:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ akoiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee Mwathani, o kĩambĩrĩria-inĩ, nĩwaarire mĩthingi ya thĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o narĩo igũrũ nĩ wĩra wa moko maku.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 34:4">Isa 34:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Icio nĩgũthira igaathira, no wee nĩgũtũũra ũgaatũũra;</para>
  <para style="q2">igaathira o ta nguo.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 102:25-27">Thab 102:25-27</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũgaacikũnja o ta ũrĩa nguo ndaaya ikũnjagwo;</para>
  <para style="q2">ikaagarũrũka o ta ũrĩa nguo igarũrũkaga.</para>
  <para style="q1">No wee ndũgarũrũkaga,</para>
  <para style="q2">na mĩaka yaku ndĩrĩ hĩndĩ ĩgaathira.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 110:1">Thab 110:1</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 22:44">Math 22:44</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, nĩ mũraika ũrĩkũ Ngai arĩ eera atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">“Ikara thĩ guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũrĩo,</para>
  <para style="q1">nginya rĩrĩa ngaatũma thũ ciaku</para>
  <para style="q2">ituĩke gaturwa ka makinya maku”?</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 103:20">Thab 103:20</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 10:17">Mar 10:17</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ araika othe ti maroho ma gũtungata, matũmĩtwo matungatagĩre arĩa makaagaya ũhonokio?</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gwathwo Gũthikĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, nĩtwagĩrĩirwo kũrũmbũiya mũno ũhoro ũrĩa twanaigua, nĩguo tũtikae gũtũgũgio tweherio kuuma harĩ guo. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 33:12">Gũcook 33:12</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 7:53">Atũm 7:53</ref></char></note>Tondũ-rĩ, angĩkorwo ũhoro ũrĩa waririo nĩ araika warĩ mũrũmu-rĩ, na mũndũ o wothe wareganaga na ũhoro ũcio na akaũremera nĩaherithagio o ũrĩa kwagĩrĩire-rĩ, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:2">Luk 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 10:29">Ahib 10:29</ref></char></note>tũngĩkĩaga atĩa kũherithio tũngĩnyarara ũhonokio mũnene ũũ? Ũhonokio ũyũ, ũrĩa waambire kũhunjio nĩ Mwathani, nĩwacookire gwĩkĩrwo hinya kũrĩ ithuĩ nĩ andũ arĩa maamũiguire. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:4">1Akor 12:4</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:9">Aef 2:9</ref></char></note>Ningĩ Ngai agĩĩkĩra ũhoro ũyũ ũira atĩ nĩ wa ma na ũndũ wa kuonania marũũri na morirũ, o na kũringa ciama cia mĩthemba mĩingĩ, na akĩheana iheo cia Roho Mũtheru kũrĩ andũ kũringana na wendi wake.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ gũtuuo ta Ariũ a Nyina</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>Thĩ ĩrĩa tũkwaria ũhoro wayo, araika tio maaheetwo wathani wayo. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:6-8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 8:4-6">Thab 8:4-6</ref></char></note>No nĩ harĩ mũndũ mũna ũheanĩte ũira handũ hamwe akoiga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Mũndũ akĩrĩ kĩ tondũ ũikaraga ũkĩmwĩciiragia,</para>
  <para style="q2">nake mũrũ wa mũndũ akĩrĩ kĩ atĩ nĩkĩo ũmũmenyagĩrĩra?</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Watũmire atigie o hanini aiganane na araika,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ũkĩmũhumba thũmbĩ ya riiri o na gĩtĩĩo,</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>na ũkĩiga indo ciothe rungu rwa magũrũ make aciathage.”</para>
  <para style="m">Nake akĩiga indo ciothe rungu rwa mũndũ-rĩ, hatirĩ kĩndũ o na kĩrĩkũ Ngai aatigire gĩtarĩ watho-inĩ wa mũndũ. No rĩu tũtionaga indo ciothe irĩ watho-inĩ wa mũndũ. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 3:13">Atũm 3:13</ref></char></note>No tuonaga Jesũ, ũrĩa gwa kahinda kanini watuĩtwo mũnini gũkĩra araika, no rĩu ekĩrĩtwo thũmbĩ ya riiri na ya gĩtĩĩo nĩ tondũ nĩanyariirĩkire na agĩkua, nĩgeetha, nĩ ũndũ wa Wega wa Ngai atuĩke wa gũcama gĩkuũ handũ ha andũ othe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 11:36">Arom 11:36</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:26">Luk 24:26</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩ kwagĩrĩire atĩ Ngai, ũrĩa wombire indo ciothe na itũũraga nĩ ũndũ wake-rĩ, atũme mwambĩrĩria wa ũhonokio wao aagĩrĩre kũna kũna na ũndũ wa kũnyamario nĩguo arehe ciana nyingĩ riiri-inĩ wake. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 13:12">Ahib 13:12</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 28:10">Math 28:10</ref></char></note>Jesũ ũrĩa ũtũmaga andũ matuĩke atheru, o hamwe na acio matuĩtwo atheru, othe matuĩkaga andũ a nyũmba ĩmwe. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Jesũ ndaconokaga akĩmeeta ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 22:22">Thab 22:22</ref></char></note>Akoiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Nĩngoimbũra rĩĩtwa rĩaku kũrĩ ariũ na aarĩ a Baba;</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩngainaga nyĩmbo cia gũkũgooca ndĩ kĩũngano-inĩ.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 8:17-18">Isa 8:17-18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ningĩ akoiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Niĩ ngũiga mwĩhoko wakwa harĩ Ngai.”</para>
  <para style="m">O na ningĩ akoiga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Niĩ ũyũ haha, na ciana iria Ngai aaheete.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:14">Joh 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 3:15">Kĩam 3:15</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:8">1Joh 3:8</ref></char>
    </note>Kuona atĩ ciana icio irĩ na mwĩrĩ na thakame-rĩ, we o nake aatuĩkire o tao mwĩrĩ-inĩ, nĩgeetha na ũndũ wa gĩkuũ gĩake ahote kwananga ũrĩa ũrĩ na hinya wa gĩkuũ, nake nĩwe mũcukani, <verse number="15" style="v"/>na ohore arĩa matũire mohetwo ũkombo-inĩ matukũ mao mothe nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra gĩkuũ. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 3:8">Luk 3:8</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ti-itherũ ti araika ateithagia, no ateithagia rũciaro rwa Iburahĩmu. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 4:14">Ahib 4:14</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 4:15">15</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 3:25">Arom 3:25</ref></char></note>Na nĩ ũndũ ũcio no nginya angĩahaananirio na ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe maũndũ-inĩ mothe, nĩguo atuĩke mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene ũiyũrĩtwo nĩ tha na mwĩhokeku agĩtungatĩra Ngai, na nĩguo arute horohio nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo we mwene nĩathĩĩnĩkire rĩrĩa aageragio-rĩ, nĩahotaga gũteithia andũ arĩa mageragio.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ nĩ Mũnene gũkĩra Musa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 2:11">Ahib 2:11</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:12">1Tim 6:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, inyuĩ ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ atheru, o inyuĩ mũgwatanĩire ũhoro wa gwĩtwo kũrĩa kuumĩte na igũrũ, mwĩcũranagiei ũhoro wa Jesũ, o we mũtũmwo na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene ũrĩa tuumbũraga ũhoro wake. <verse number="2" style="v"/>We aarĩ mwĩhokeku kũrĩ ũrĩa wamwamũrire, o ta ũrĩa Musa aarĩ mwĩhokeku maũndũ-inĩ mothe ma nyũmba ya Ngai. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Jesũ nĩonekanĩte aagĩrĩire kũheo gĩtĩĩo kĩnene gũkĩra Musa, o ta ũrĩa mwaki wa nyũmba aagĩrĩirwo nĩ gũtĩĩo gũkĩra nyũmba yo nyene. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo nyũmba o yothe nĩĩrĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wamĩakire, no Ngai nĩwe mwaki wa indo ciothe. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 14:31">Thaam 14:31</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 12:7">Ndar 12:7</ref></char></note>Nake Musa, aarĩ mwĩhokeku maũndũ-inĩ mothe ma nyũmba ya Ngai arĩ o ndungata, agakĩrutaga ũira wa maũndũ marĩa makaaheanwo thuutha-inĩ. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 1:2">Ahib 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 5:2">Arom 5:2</ref></char></note>No Kristũ arĩ Mũriũ aarĩ mwĩhokeku na akarũgamĩrĩra nyũmba ya Ngai. Na ithuĩ tũrĩ nyũmba ĩyo yake, tũngĩikara tũrũmĩtie ũmĩrĩru witũ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩa twĩrahagĩra.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũkaanio kwaga Gwĩtĩkia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 4:3">Ahib 4:3</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 4:5">5</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 95:7-11">Thab 95:7-11</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, o ta ũrĩa Roho Mũtheru oigaga, atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ũmũthĩ, mũngĩigua mũgambo wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 4:7">Ahib 4:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>mũtikoomie ngoro cianyu</para>
  <para style="q1">ta hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwanemeire,</para>
  <para style="q2">andũ makĩĩngeria marĩ kũu werũ-inĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 7:36">Atũm 7:36</ref>
      </char>
    </note>kũrĩa maithe manyu maangeririe na makĩndoria,</para>
  <para style="q2">na makĩona ciĩko ciakwa, ihinda rĩa mĩaka mĩrongo ĩna.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩkĩo ndaarakarĩire rũciaro rũu, ngĩkiuga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Ngoro cia andũ aya itururaga hĩndĩ ciothe,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matirĩ maamenya njĩra ciakwa.’</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngĩĩhĩta na mwĩhĩtwa ndakarĩte, ngiuga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Matirĩ hĩndĩ magaatoonya kĩhurũko-inĩ gĩakwa.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mwĩmenyererei hatikagĩe o na ũmwe wanyu ũrĩ na ngoro ĩĩhagia na ĩtetĩkagia, ĩrĩa ĩgarũrũkaga, ĩgatigana na Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ muoyo. <verse number="13" style="v"/>No ũmanagĩrĩriai mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ o mũthenya, o rĩrĩa rĩothe mũthenya ũrĩĩtagwo Ũmũthĩ, nĩgeetha gũtikagĩe o na ũmwe wanyu ũkũũmio ngoro nĩ ũndũ wa kũheenererio nĩ mehia. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 3:6">Ahib 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 3:12">Aef 3:12</ref></char></note>Tondũ ũcio, tũngĩrũmia wega mwĩhoko ũrĩa twarĩ naguo kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria nginya ithirĩro-rĩ, nĩtũgaatuĩka a kũgwatanĩra hamwe na Kristũ. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 95:7-8">Thab 95:7-8</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 3:7">Ahib 3:7</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 3:8">8</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa kwĩrĩtwo, atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ũmũthĩ, mũngĩigua mũgambo wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũtikoomie ngoro cianyu</para>
  <para style="q1">ta hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwanemeire.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 14:2">Ndar 14:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ andũ arĩkũ acio maaiguire na makĩmũkararia? Githĩ ti arĩa othe moimĩte Misiri matongoretio nĩ Musa? <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 106:26">Thab 106:26</ref></char></note>Ningĩ-rĩ, nĩ andũ arĩkũ aarakarĩire mĩaka ĩyo mĩrongo ĩna? Githĩ ti arĩa meehirie, na magĩkua, o arĩa ciimba ciao ciagũire kũu werũ-inĩ? <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 14:20-23">Ndar 14:20-23</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 4:6">Ahib 4:6</ref></char></note>Ningĩ-rĩ, nĩ andũ arĩkũ Ngai ehĩtire na mwĩhĩtwa atĩ gũtirĩ hĩndĩ magaatoonya ũhurũko-inĩ wake, tiga o andũ acio maaregire kũmwathĩkĩra? <verse number="19" style="v"/>Tũgakĩona atĩrĩ, matiahotire gũtoonya kuo nĩ ũndũ wa kwaga gwĩtĩkia kwao.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Thabatũ ya Kũhurũka ya Andũ a Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 12:15">Ahib 12:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, kuona atĩ kĩĩranĩro gĩa gũtoonya ũhurũko-inĩ wake kĩrĩ o ho-rĩ, nĩtwĩmenyererei gũtikagĩe o na ũmwe wanyu ũtagagĩkinyĩra. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo o na ithuĩ nĩtũhunjĩirio Ũhoro-ũyũ-Mwega o tao; no ũhoro ũrĩa maaiguire ndũigana kũmaguna, tondũ arĩa maũiguire matiawamũkĩrire na wĩtĩkio. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 95:11">Thab 95:11</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, ithuĩ arĩa twĩtĩkĩtie nĩ ithuĩ tũtoonyaga kĩhurũko-inĩ kĩu, o ta ũrĩa Ngai oigire atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngĩĩhĩta na mwĩhĩtwa ndakarĩte, ngiuga atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">‘Matirĩ hĩndĩ magaatoonya kĩhurũko-inĩ gĩakwa.’ ”</para>
  <para style="m">O na gũtuĩka wĩra wake nĩwathirĩte kuuma o rĩrĩa thĩ yombirwo. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:2">Kĩam 2:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩ harĩ handũ hana aarĩtie ũhoro wa mũthenya wa mũgwanja, akoiga atĩrĩ: “Nake Ngai akĩhurũka mũthenya wa mũgwanja, agĩtigana na wĩra wake wothe.” <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 95:11">Thab 95:11</ref></char></note>O na ningĩ hau mbere nĩoigĩte atĩrĩ, “Matirĩ hĩndĩ magaatoonya ũhurũko-inĩ wakwa.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 3:18">Ahib 3:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩtũkuona atĩ nĩ kũrĩ amwe matigaire gũtoonya kĩhurũko-inĩ kĩu kĩeranĩirwo, nĩgũkorwo arĩa maahunjĩirio Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega mbere matiatoonyire tondũ nĩmagire gwathĩka. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 95:7-8">Thab 95:7-8</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, o rĩngĩ Ngai akĩamũra mũthenya mũna, akĩwĩĩta Ũmũthĩ, thuutha wa matukũ maingĩ gũthira rĩrĩa aaririe na kanua ka Daudi, ta ũrĩa oigĩte hau mbere atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ũmũthĩ, mũngĩigua mũgambo wake,</para>
  <para style="q2">mũtikoomie ngoro cianyu.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 22:4">Josh 22:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tondũ korwo Joshua nĩamaheete ũhurũko-rĩ, Ngai ndangĩacookire kwaria ũhoro wa mũthenya ũngĩ thuutha ũcio. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Tondũ ũcio nĩgũtigaire Thabatũ ya kũhurũka ya andũ a Ngai; <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 4:4">Ahib 4:4</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũtoonyaga kĩhurũko-inĩ kĩa Ngai o nake nĩahurũkaga agatigana na wĩra wake, o ta ũrĩa Ngai aahurũkire agĩtigana na wĩra wake. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 3:18">Ahib 3:18</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, nĩtwĩrutanĩrie na kĩyo gũtoonya ũhurũko-inĩ ũcio, nĩgeetha gũtikanagĩe mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũkaagũa nĩ ũndũ wa kũrũmĩrĩra kĩonereria kĩa ũremi wao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 4:14">Mar 4:14</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 7:38">Atũm 7:38</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:17">Aef 6:17</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo ũhoro wa Ngai ũrĩ muoyo na ũrĩ hinya. Nĩ mũũgĩ gũkĩra rũhiũ rwa njora rũnooretwo mĩena yeerĩ, ũgatheeca ũkagayũkania muoyo na roho, o na ũkagayania marũngo na maguta marĩa makoragwo mahĩndĩ-inĩ, na ningĩ ũgatuĩra meciiria na matua ma ngoro. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 33:13-15">Thab 33:13-15</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ kĩndũ o na kĩmwe kĩa iria ciombirwo kĩhithĩtwo kuuma maitho-inĩ ma Ngai. Indo ciothe nĩhumbũrie na ikaguũrio mbere ya maitho ma ũrĩa tũkaahe ũhoro witũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai Ũrĩa Mũnene Mũno</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 3:1">Ahib 3:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, kuona atĩ tũrĩ na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene mũno ũrĩa ũhungurĩte agakinya o igũrũ, na nĩwe Jesũ mũrũ wa Ngai-rĩ, nĩtũrũmiei na hinya wĩtĩkio ũrĩa tuumbũraga. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 5:21">2Akor 5:21</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo tũtirĩ na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene ũtangĩhota gũtũiguĩra tha ũhũthũ-inĩ witũ, no nĩ tũrĩ na ũmwe wanagerio ikĩro-inĩ ciothe o ta ithuĩ, no ndaigana kwĩhia. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 3:12">Aef 3:12</ref></char></note>Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, nĩtũkuhĩrĩriei gĩtĩ kĩa Ũnene kĩrĩa kĩa Wega wake tũrĩ na ũũmĩrĩru, nĩgeetha tũkaiguĩrwo tha, na tuone Wega wake wa gũtũteithagia hĩndĩ ĩrĩa tũbatarĩte.</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 8:3">Ahib 8:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩu-rĩ, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene o wothe athuuragwo kuuma gatagatĩ ka andũ na agatuuo wa kũmarũgamĩrĩra maũndũ-inĩ marĩa makoniĩ Ngai, nĩguo arutage maruta na magongona nĩ ũndũ wa kũhoroheria mehia. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 29:24">Isa 29:24</ref></char></note>Nake nĩahotaga gũkirĩrĩria arĩa matarĩ na ũmenyo o na arĩa maturuurĩte, kuona atĩ o nake nĩarĩ ũhũthũ wake. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo ũtũmaga arute magongona ma kũhoroheria mehia make mwene, o ta ũrĩa amarutaga nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 28:1">Thaam 28:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ wĩheaga gĩtĩĩo kĩu we mwene; no nginya akorwo etĩtwo nĩ Ngai, o ta ũrĩa Harũni eetirwo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 2:7">Thab 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 8:54">Joh 8:54</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, o nake Kristũ ndaigana kwĩyoera ũgooci wa gũtuĩka mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene. No nĩ Ngai wamwĩrire atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa;</para>
  <para style="q2">ũmũthĩ nĩndatuĩka Thoguo.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 110:4">Thab 110:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na handũ hangĩ oigĩte atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee ũrĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai nginya tene,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa Melikisedeki aatariĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 27:46">Math 27:46</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 27:50">50</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 22:24">Thab 22:24</ref></char>
    </note>Matukũ-inĩ marĩa Jesũ aatũũraga gũkũ thĩ-rĩ, nĩahooyaga na agathaitha Ngai, agĩkayaga mũno agĩitaga maithori kũrĩ ũcio ũngĩahotire kũmũhonokia kuuma gĩkuũ-inĩ, na nĩaiguagwo nĩ ũndũ wa kwĩnyiihia gwake. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 1:2">Ahib 1:2</ref></char></note>O na gũtuĩka aarĩ mũriũ, nĩerutire gwathĩka nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa aanyariirĩkire, <verse number="9" style="v"/>na aarĩkia gũtuuo mwagĩrĩru kũna, agĩtuĩka kĩhumo kĩa ũhonokio ũrĩa ũtagaathira harĩ arĩa othe mamwathĩkagĩra, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 5:5">Ahib 5:5</ref></char></note>nake Ngai akĩmũtua mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene o ta ũrĩa Melikisedeki aatariĩ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũtaarwo nĩguo Tũtikagwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩtũrĩ na maũndũ maingĩ tũngĩmwĩra makoniĩ ũhoro ũyũ, no nĩ hinya kũmũtaarĩria tondũ mũtinyiitaga maũndũ narua. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 3:2">1Akor 3:2</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, o na gũtuĩka rĩu mwagĩrĩirwo nĩgũkorwo mũrĩ arutani-rĩ, nĩmũbatarĩte mũndũ wa kũmũruta maũndũ marĩa mwarutĩtwo kĩambĩrĩria ma kiugo kĩa Ngai o rĩngĩ. Inyuĩ mũbataire kũheo iria, no ti irio nyũmũ! <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 14:20">1Akor 14:20</ref></char></note>Mũndũ o wothe ũnyuuaga iria, tondũ no gakenge-rĩ, ndangĩmenya wega ũhoro wa ũrutani wa ũthingu. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 2:6">1Akor 2:6</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 7:15">Isa 7:15</ref></char></note>No irio iria nyũmũ nĩ cia andũ arĩa agima, arĩa nĩ ũndũ wa kũmenyera gũcihũthĩra kaingĩ, nĩmerutĩte gũkũũrana wega na ũũru.</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩtũtiganei na morutani marĩa ma kĩambĩrĩria ma ũhoro wa Kristũ, na tũthiĩ na mbere na gũkũra, na tũtige kwambĩrĩria gwaka mũthingi rĩngĩ wa kũrutana ũhoro wa kwĩrira nĩ ũndũ wa ciĩko iria cierekagĩria mũndũ gĩkuũ-inĩ, na ũrutani wa gwĩtĩkia thĩinĩ wa Ngai, <verse number="2" style="v"/>na morutani ma ũbatithio, na ma kũigĩrĩrwo moko, o na ma kũriũka kwa arĩa akuũ, o na ma gũtuĩrwo ciira wa tene na tene. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:21">Atũm 18:21</ref></char></note>Na noguo tũrĩĩkaga, Ngai angĩĩtĩkĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 10:32">Ahib 10:32</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:8">Aef 2:8</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 3:2">Agal 3:2</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, nĩ ũndũ ũrĩ hinya mũno kũrĩ andũ arĩa maanathererwo nĩ ũtheri, na magacama kĩheo kĩrĩa kiumĩte igũrũ, na magakorwo matuĩtwo a ngwatanĩro ya Roho Mũtheru, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 34:8">Thab 34:8</ref></char></note>o acio macamĩte wega wa kiugo kĩa Ngai na maahinya ma ihinda rĩrĩa rĩgooka, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 5:16">1Joh 5:16</ref></char></note>andũ acio mangĩgũa na matigane na maũndũ macio-rĩ, gũtingĩhoteka kũmacookia rĩngĩ merire, nĩ tondũ nĩ kwambithia marambithia Mũrũ wa Ngai mũtĩ igũrũ o rĩngĩ, na makamũnyararithia kũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Mũgũnda ũrĩa uragĩrwo nĩ mbura kaingĩ na ũgacooka ũgaciara maciaro mega ma kũguna arĩa marĩmĩirwo-rĩ, nĩũrathimagwo nĩ Ngai. <verse number="8" style="v"/>No mũgũnda ũrĩa ũkũraga mĩigua na mahiũ ma nyeki-inĩ nĩ wa tũhũ, na ũrĩ ũgwati-inĩ wa kwĩrehithĩria kĩrumi. Marigĩrĩrio-inĩ nĩgũcinwo ũgaacinwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:4">1Akor 10:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Arata akwa nyendete mũno, o na tũkĩaragia ũguo, ha ũhoro wanyu-rĩ, nĩtwĩrĩgĩrĩire maũndũ mega kũrĩ macio, o marĩa marehanaga na ũhonokio. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 10:40">Math 10:40</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 10:42">42</ref></char></note>Tondũ Ngai ndaagĩte kĩhooto; ndakaariganĩrwo nĩ wĩra wanyu o na wendo ũrĩa muonanĩtie nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩrĩa mwateithagia andũ arĩa aamũre, o na rĩu no mũrathiĩ na mbere na kũmateithia. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 3:6">Ahib 3:6</ref></char></note>Tũngĩenda mũndũ o mũndũ wanyu onanie kĩyo o ta kĩu o nginya mũthia, nĩguo mũkaahingĩrio maũndũ marĩa mũtũire mwĩrĩgĩrĩire. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Tũtikwenda mũtuĩke igũũta, no tũkwenda mwĩgerekanagie na andũ, arĩa nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia na gũkirĩrĩria kwao nĩkuo gũtũmaga magaĩrwo maũndũ marĩa meranĩirwo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũũma wa Kĩĩranĩro kĩa Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 1:73">Luk 1:73</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Ngai eerĩire Iburahĩmu kĩĩranĩro gĩake, eehĩtire akĩĩgwetaga we mwene, nĩgũkorwo gũtiarĩ na ũngĩ mũnene kũrĩ we wa kwĩhĩta nake, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 22:17">Kĩam 22:17</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 22:11">Thaam 22:11</ref></char></note>akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ nĩngũkũrathima na ngũhe njiaro nyingĩ.” <verse number="15" style="v"/>Na nĩ ũndũ ũcio, thuutha wa Iburahĩmu gweterera akirĩrĩirie-rĩ, nĩaheirwo kĩrĩa eerĩirwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Tondũ rĩĩrĩ, andũ mehĩtaga na mũndũ ũrĩa mũnene kũmakĩra, naguo mwĩhĩtwa ũgakindĩra ũrĩa kwĩrĩtwo, na ũgakĩniina ngarari ciothe. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 4:16">Arom 4:16</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 11:9">Ahib 11:9</ref></char></note>Na tondũ Ngai nĩendaga kuonania hatarĩ nganja kũrĩ agai a maũndũ marĩa meranĩirwo atĩ itua rĩake rĩrĩa aatuĩte rĩtingĩgarũrũka-rĩ, nĩakindĩrire ũhoro ũcio na mwĩhĩtwa. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ngai eekire ũguo na ũndũ wa maũndũ meerĩ matangĩgarũrĩka, o marĩa gũtangĩhoteka Ngai aheenanie namo, nĩgeetha ithuĩ arĩa tuonete handũ ha kũũrĩra twĩgwatĩre kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩa tũheetwo, tũhote kũũmĩrĩria mũno. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 16:2">Alaw 16:2</ref></char></note>Kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro gĩkĩ tũrĩ nakĩo kĩhaana ta nanga ya ngoro, nakĩo nĩ kĩrũmu, na nĩ kĩa ma. Nakĩo gĩtoonyaga handũ-harĩa-haamũre thuutha wa gĩtama kĩrĩa kĩnene, <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 4:14">Ahib 4:14</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 5:6">Ahib 5:6</ref></char></note>o harĩa Jesũ, ũrĩa wathiire mbere iitũ, aatoonyire ithenya riitũ. Nake nĩatuĩkĩte mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene o nginya tene, o ta ũrĩa Melikisedeki aatariĩ.</para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Melikisedeki ũrĩa Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 76:2">Thab 76:2</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 5:7">Mar 5:7</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 14:18-20">Kĩam 14:18-20</ref></char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ, Melikisedeki ũcio aarĩ mũthamaki wa Salemu na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, o Ngai-Ũrĩa-ũrĩ-Igũrũ-Mũno. Nĩwe watũngire Iburahĩmu akĩinũka aarĩkia kũhoota athamaki, na akĩmũrathima, <verse number="2" style="v"/>nake Iburahĩmu akĩmũhe gĩcunjĩ gĩa ikũmi kĩa indo ciothe. Rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩgĩtaũrwo mbere nĩ kuuga “mũthamaki wa ũthingu”; ningĩ “mũthamaki wa Salemu” nĩ kuuga “mũthamaki wa thayũ”. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 4:3">Math 4:3</ref></char></note>Ndaarĩ na ithe kana nyina, kana kĩruka gĩake, na ndaarĩ na kĩambĩrĩria kĩa matukũ kana mũthia wa muoyo wake, nĩ ũndũ ũcio, we ahaana ta Mũrũ wa Ngai, egũtũũra arĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai nginya tene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 14:20">Kĩam 14:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ta mwĩciirie ũrĩa aarĩ mũnene: Atĩ o na ithe witũ Iburahĩmu nĩamũgaĩire gĩcunjĩ gĩa ikũmi kĩa indo iria aatahĩte! <verse number="5" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, watho uugĩte atĩ andũ a rũciaro rwa Lawi arĩa matuĩkaga athĩnjĩri-Ngai metagie gĩcunjĩ gĩa ikũmi kuuma kũrĩ andũ, ũguo nĩ kuuga ariũ a ithe wao, o na gwatuĩka ariũ a ithe wao nĩ a rũciaro rwa Iburahĩmu. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 14:19-20">Kĩam 14:19-20</ref></char></note>No mũndũ ũcio ndaarĩ wa rũciaro rwa Lawi, no nĩamũkĩrire gĩcunjĩ gĩa ikũmi kuuma kũrĩ Iburahĩmu, na akĩrathima ũcio werĩirwo ciĩranĩro. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Na hatirĩ nganja atĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mũnini nĩwe ũrathimagwo nĩ ũrĩa mũnene. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 5:6">Ahib 5:6</ref></char></note>Tũgakĩona atĩ, mwena ũmwe gĩcunjĩ kĩu gĩa ikũmi kĩũnganagio nĩ andũ arĩa macookaga gũkua, na nĩo Alawii; naguo mwena ũcio ũngĩ, kĩrutagĩrwo mũndũ ũrĩa uumbũrĩtwo ũhoro wake atĩ atũũraga o muoyo. <verse number="9" style="v"/>O na mũndũ no oige atĩ Lawi, ũcio ũrutagĩrwo gĩcunjĩ kĩu gĩa ikũmi, we mwene nĩarutire gĩcunjĩ kĩu na njĩra ya Iburahĩmu, <verse number="10" style="v"/>tondũ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Melikisedeki aacemanirie na Iburahĩmu, Lawi aarĩ mũthiimo-inĩ wa ithe ũcio wa tene.</para>
  <para style="s1">Jesũ ahaana ta Melikisedeki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 7:18-19">Ahib 7:18-19</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 8:7">Ahib 8:7</ref></char>
    </note>Korwo ũkinyanĩru kũna nĩũngĩonekanire na njĩra ya ũthĩnjĩri Ngai wa Alawii-rĩ, (nĩ ũndũ kĩrĩndĩ kĩaheirwo watho na njĩra ĩyo), gwakĩrĩ bata ũngĩ ũrĩkũ gũũke mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũngĩ, ũtariĩ ta Melikisedeki, na ndatuĩke ta wa nyũmba ya Harũni? <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo ũhoro wa ũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũngĩgarũrĩrwo-rĩ, o naguo watho no nginya ũgarũrĩrwo. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nake mũndũ ũrĩa maũndũ maya maarĩtio nĩ ũndũ wake oimĩte mũhĩrĩga-inĩ ũngĩ, ũrĩa gũtarĩ mũndũ waguo ũrĩ watungatĩra Ngai kĩgongona-inĩ. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 11:1">Isa 11:1</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩkũĩkaine wega atĩ Mwathani witũ oimire mũhĩrĩga-inĩ wa Juda, na ha ũhoro wa mũhĩrĩga ũcio-rĩ, Musa ndaigana kuuga ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũkoniĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, ũhoro ũrĩa twarĩtie no ũmenyeke wega makĩria angĩkorwo mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũngĩ ũtariĩ ta Melikisedeki nĩonekanĩte, <verse number="16" style="v"/>ũrĩa ũtuĩkĩte mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, na ti kũringana na mũtugo wa rũciaro rwake, no nĩ tondũ wa ũhoti wa muoyo ũrĩa ũtathiraga. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 110:4">Thab 110:4</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩkuumbũrĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee ũrĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai nginya tene,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa Melikisedeki aatariĩ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 8:3">Arom 8:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Watho wa mbere nĩũtiganĩtwo naguo tondũ ndwarĩ na hinya na ũkaaga bata <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 3:20">Arom 3:20</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 4:16">Ahib 4:16</ref></char></note>(nĩgũkorwo watho ndũrĩ ũndũ watũmire wagĩrĩre kũna), no nĩtũheetwo kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩega makĩria kĩrĩa gĩtũhotithagia gũkuhĩrĩria Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Na ũndũ ũyũ ndwekirwo hatarĩ mwĩhĩtwa! Andũ acio angĩ nĩmatuĩkaga athĩnjĩri-Ngai hatarĩ mwĩhĩtwa, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:29">Arom 11:29</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 110:4">Thab 110:4</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 5:6">Ahib 5:6</ref></char></note>nowe aatuĩkire mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai na mwĩhĩtwa, rĩrĩa Ngai aamwĩrire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Jehova nĩehĩtĩte,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndangĩĩricũkwo, akoiga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">‘Wee ũrĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai nginya tene.’ ”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa mwĩhĩtwa ũyũ, Jesũ nĩatuĩkĩte mũrũgamĩrĩri wa kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩega makĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Ningĩ-rĩ, nĩgũkoretwo na athĩnjĩri-Ngai aingĩ ta acio hau mbere, nĩgũkorwo nĩmakuaga magakĩgirio gũthiĩ na mbere na ũtungata ũcio. <verse number="24" style="v"/>No tondũ Jesũ atũũraga muoyo nginya tene-rĩ, ũthĩnjĩri-Ngai wake nĩ wa gũtũũra nginya tene. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:34">Arom 8:34</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩahotaga kũhonokia kũna arĩa othe mokaga kũrĩ Ngai magereire harĩ we, nĩgũkorwo egũtũũra amathaithanagĩrĩra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 4:14">Ahib 4:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tondũ nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũgĩe na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene ta ũcio, atũhingagĩrie bata witũ, na akorwo arĩ mũtheru, na atarĩ ũcuuke, kana rĩhia, na aamũranĩtio na ehia, o na agatũũgĩrio igũrũ rĩa igũrũ. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 5:1">Ahib 5:1</ref></char></note>We ndekũbatara kũruta magongona mũthenya o mũthenya ta ũrĩa athĩnjĩri-Ngai anene acio angĩ meekaga, mbere nĩ ũndũ wa mehia make mwene, na thuutha ũcio nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ. We nĩarutire igongona nĩ ũndũ wa mehia mao ihinda o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana hĩndĩ ĩrĩa eerutire we mwene. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 2:10">Ahib 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 5:2">Ahib 5:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo watho ũtuaga andũ matarĩ hinya athĩnjĩri Ngai anene; no mwĩhĩtwa, ũrĩa wokire thuutha wa watho, nĩwaamũrire Mũriũ, ũrĩa ũtuĩkĩte mwagĩrĩru kũna nginya tene.</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai Ũrĩa Mũnene wa Kĩrĩkanĩro Kĩerũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Atĩrĩrĩ, ũhoro ũrĩa tũraaria nĩ atĩ: Nĩ tũrĩ na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai-mũnene, ũrĩa ũikarĩte thĩ guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo gwa gĩtĩ kĩa Ũnene kĩa ũthamaki wa igũrũ, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 9:11">Ahib 9:11</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 9:24">24</ref></char></note>nake nĩ mũtungatĩri wa handũ-harĩa-haamũre, o kũu hema-inĩ ya gũtũnganwo ĩrĩa ya ma ĩrĩa yaakirwo nĩ Mwathani, no ti mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 5:1">Ahib 5:1</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 9:14">Ahib 9:14</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene o wothe aathuuragwo nĩguo arutage iheo na magongona, na nĩ ũndũ ũcio o nake no nginya akorwo arĩ na kĩndũ gĩa kũruta. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Korwo arĩ o gũkũ thĩ-rĩ, ndangĩrĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, nĩgũkorwo nĩ kũrĩ andũ arĩa marutaga iheo iria ciathanĩtwo nĩ watho. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:17">Akol 2:17</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 25:40">Thaam 25:40</ref></char></note>Nao matungataga mũhianĩre wa handũ-harĩa-haamũre na kĩĩruru kĩa maũndũ marĩa marĩ igũrũ. Ũndũ ũcio nĩguo watũmire Musa ataarwo hĩndĩ ĩrĩa eeharagĩria gwaka Hema-ya-Gũtũnganwo, akĩĩrwo atĩrĩ: “Menyerera wone nĩwathondeka indo icio ciothe kũringana na mũhianĩre ũrĩa wonirio ũrĩ kĩrĩma-inĩ.” <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:20">Agal 3:20</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, ũtungata ũrĩa Jesũ aheetwo nĩũkĩrĩte wao, o ta ũrĩa kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa arĩ we mũiguithania wakĩo gĩkĩrĩte kĩrĩa gĩkũrũ, na ningĩ kĩhaandĩtwo na ciĩranĩro njega makĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 7:11">Ahib 7:11</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 7:18">18</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo kĩrĩkanĩro kĩa mbere gĩtangĩarĩ na mahĩtia, gũtingĩagĩire bata wa gwetha kĩngĩ gĩa keerĩ. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 22:20">Luk 22:20</ref></char></note>No Ngai nĩoonire andũ marĩ na mahĩtia, akiuga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Matukũ nĩmarooka,</para>
  <para style="q2">rĩrĩa ngaarĩkanĩra kĩrĩkanĩro kĩerũ</para>
  <para style="q1">na nyũmba ya Isiraeli,</para>
  <para style="q2">o hamwe na nyũmba ya Juda, nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Nakĩo kĩrĩkanĩro kĩu gĩtikahaana ta kĩrĩkanĩro</para>
  <para style="q2">kĩrĩa ndaarĩkanĩire na maithe mao ma tene</para>
  <para style="q1">rĩrĩa ndaamanyiitire na guoko,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngĩmatongoria, ngĩmaruta bũrũri wa Misiri,</para>
  <para style="q1">na tondũ matiigana gũikara marĩ ehokeku harĩ kĩrĩkanĩro gĩakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">na niĩ ngĩmahutatĩra,</para>
  <para style="q4">ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 10:16">Ahib 10:16</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 11:20">Ezek 11:20</ref></char>
    </note>Gĩkĩ nĩkĩo kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa ngaarĩkanĩra na nyũmba ya Isiraeli</para>
  <para style="q2">ihinda rĩu rĩathira, nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩngekĩra watho wakwa meciiria-inĩ mao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ningĩ ndĩwaandĩke ngoro-inĩ ciao.</para>
  <para style="q1">Na niĩ ngaatuĩka Ngai wao,</para>
  <para style="q2">nao matuĩke andũ akwa.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 54:13">Isa 54:13</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 6:45">Joh 6:45</ref></char>
    </note>Gũtigacooka gũkorwo na mũndũ ũkũruta ũrĩa ũngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">kana mũndũ arute mũrũ wa ithe amwĩre atĩrĩ, ‘Menyana na Mwathani,’</para>
  <para style="q1">tondũ andũ othe nĩmagakorwo maamenyete,</para>
  <para style="q2">kuuma ũrĩa mũnini mũno wao nginya ũrĩa mũnene.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 10:17">Ahib 10:17</ref>; <ref loc="JER 31:31-34">Jer 31:31-34</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩngamarekera waganu wao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndigacooka kũririkana mehia mao.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 22:20">Luk 22:20</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:17">2Akor 5:17</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, rĩrĩa ekwaria ũhoro wa kĩrĩkanĩro kĩerũ-rĩ, nĩgũtua aatuire kĩrĩa kĩa mbere gĩkũrũ; na kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩrakũra-rĩ, gĩtuĩkaga gĩa gũthira, gĩkabuĩria o biũ.</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Kũhooya Ngai thĩinĩ wa Hema-ya-Gũtũnganwo ya Gũkũ Thĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 25:8">Thaam 25:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩu-rĩ, kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩa mbere nĩ kĩarĩ na mawatho maakoniĩ ũhoro wa kũhooya Ngai, o na ningĩ nĩ kwarĩ na handũ-harĩa-haamũre gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 25:23-29">Thaam 25:23-29</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 24:5-8">Alaw 24:5-8</ref></char></note>Nĩ kwarĩ na hema yathondeketwo, na kanyũmba kayo ka mbere nĩ haarĩ na mũtĩ ũrĩa wa gũcuuria matawa, na metha, na mĩgate ĩrĩa mĩamũre; hau nĩho heetagwo “Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru.” <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 26:31-33">Thaam 26:31-33</ref></char></note>Thuutha wa gĩtama gĩa keerĩ haarĩ na kanyũmba geetagwo, “Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru-Mũno,” <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 25:10-22">Thaam 25:10-22</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 16:32">Thaam 16:32</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 16:33">33</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 17:10">Ndar 17:10</ref></char></note>na hau nĩho haarĩ kĩgongona gĩa thahabu gĩa gũcinĩrwo ũbumba, na nĩho haarĩ ithandũkũ rĩa kĩrĩkanĩro rĩrĩa rĩahumbĩrĩtwo na thahabu kũndũ guothe. Thĩinĩ wa ithandũkũ rĩu nĩ haarĩ na nyũngũ ya thahabu yarĩ na mana, na rũthanju rwa Harũni rũrĩa rwathundũkĩte, na ihengere cia mahiga iria ciandĩkĩtwo. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Igũrũ wa ithandũkũ rĩu nĩ haarĩ na akerubi a Riiri, mahumbĩrĩte gĩtĩ-gĩa-tha. No rĩu tũtingĩhota gũtaarĩria wega rĩu ũhoro wa kĩndũ o kĩndũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 26:3">Ndar 26:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nacio indo ciothe ciarĩkia kũbangwo ũguo-rĩ, athĩnjĩri-Ngai nao maatoonyaga kanyũmba kau ka mbere hĩndĩ ciothe nĩguo marute wĩra wao wa ũtungata. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 16:11">Alaw 16:11</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 5:2">Ahib 5:2</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 5:3">3</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene nowe wiki watoonyaga kanyũmba karĩa ga thĩinĩ, na aatoonyaga o ihinda o rĩmwe mwaka, na ndangĩatoonyire atakuuĩte thakame ya kũruta igongona nĩ ũndũ wake mwene na nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma andũ marĩa meekĩte matekũmenya. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 14:6">Joh 14:6</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 10:19">Ahib 10:19</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 10:20">20</ref></char></note>Ũndũ ũyũ nĩguo Roho Mũtheru oonanagia naguo atĩ njĩra ya gũtoonya Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru-Mũno ndĩakoretwo ĩguũranĩirio ihinda rĩrĩa rĩothe hema ya mbere yarĩ ho. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 5:1">Ahib 5:1</ref></char></note>Gĩkĩ gĩkĩrĩ o kĩonereria kĩa matukũ maya tũrĩ, atĩ maruta na magongona marĩa maarutagwo matingĩahotire gũtheria thamiri ya mũndũ ũrĩa mũhooi Ngai. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 6:3">Ndar 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="COL 2:16">Akol 2:16</ref></char></note>Maũndũ macio makoniĩ o ũhoro wa kũrĩa na kũnyua, na magongona ma mĩthemba mĩingĩ ya gwĩtheria na mawatho ma na igũrũ tu, marĩa maathanĩtwo mekagwo nginya ihinda rĩrĩa maũndũ makeerũhio rĩgaakinya.</para>
  <para style="s1">Thakame ya Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 8:2">Ahib 8:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:19">Joh 2:19</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩrĩa Kristũ ookire arĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene wa maũndũ mega marĩa marĩ kuo-rĩ, nĩagereire hema-inĩ ĩrĩa nene na nginyanĩru ĩrĩa ĩtathondeketwo na moko ma andũ, naguo ũguo nĩ kuuga ti ya mũmbĩre wa thĩ ĩno. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:6">Arom 16:6</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 16:15">15</ref></char></note>Ndaatoonyire na ũndũ wa thakame ya mbũri na njaũ; nowe aatoonyire Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru-Mũno riita o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana na ũndũ wa thakame yake we mwene, arĩkĩtie gũkũũra andũ na ũkũũri ũrĩa ũtagaathira. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Thakame ya mbũri na ndegwa, na mũhu wa moori ĩcinĩtwo, ciaminjaminjĩrio arĩa marĩ na thaahu, nĩciamatheragia na ikaniina thaahu mĩĩrĩ yao. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:2">Aef 5:2</ref>; <ref loc="JER 33:8">Jer 33:8</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:16">Math 16:16</ref></char></note>Githĩ thakame ya Kristũ, ũrĩa werutire arĩ igongona rĩtarĩ kaũũgũ harĩ Ngai nĩ ũndũ wa Roho wa tene na tene, ndĩngĩgĩtheria thamiri ciitũ makĩria nĩguo itigane na ciĩko iria cierekagĩria mũndũ gĩkuũ-inĩ, nĩguo tũtungatagĩre Ngai ũrĩa ũtũũraga muoyo!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 3:20">Agal 3:20</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:28">Arom 8:28</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 20:32">Atũm 20:32</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, Kristũ nĩwe mũiguithania wa kĩrĩkanĩro kĩerũ, nĩguo arĩa metĩtwo mahote kũgaĩrwo igai rĩrĩa rĩĩranĩirwo rĩtagaathira, kuona atĩ rĩu nĩakuĩte arĩ mũkũũri wa kũmakũũra kuuma mehia-inĩ marĩa meekĩtwo kĩrĩkanĩro-inĩ kĩrĩa kĩa mbere.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Tondũ ha ũhoro ũkoniĩ kwĩgaya-rĩ, nĩ kwagĩrĩire kũmenyeke wega atĩ ũcio wĩgaĩte nĩakuĩte, <verse number="17" style="v"/>nĩ ũndũ kwĩgaya kũgĩaga na hinya rĩrĩa mũndũ ũrĩa wĩgaĩte aarĩkia gũkua; kwĩgaya gũtirĩ hinya rĩrĩa rĩothe ũrĩa wĩgaĩte arĩ muoyo. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 24:6-8">Thaam 24:6-8</ref></char></note>Ũguo noguo o nakĩo kĩrĩkanĩro kĩa mbere gĩtingĩagĩire na hinya hatarĩ thakame. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Musa aarĩkirie kũhe andũ othe maathani mothe marĩa maandĩkĩtwo watho-inĩ-rĩ, nĩoire thakame ya njaũ, o hamwe na maaĩ, na guoya mũtune, na mathĩgĩ ma mũthobi akĩminjaminjĩria ibuku rĩa gĩkũnjo o na andũ othe. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 24:8">Thaam 24:8</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:28">Math 26:28</ref></char></note>Akĩmeera atĩrĩ, “Ĩno nĩyo thakame ya kĩrĩkanĩro, kĩrĩa Ngai amwathĩte mwathĩkagĩre.” <verse number="21" style="v"/>Ningĩ o ũndũ ũmwe, akĩminjaminjĩria Hema-ya-Gũtũnganwo thakame o hamwe na indo iria ciothe ciahũthagĩrwo gũtungatĩra Ngai nacio. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 8:15">Alaw 8:15</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 17:11">Alaw 17:11</ref></char></note>Na ti-itherũ, kũringana na watho hakuhĩ indo ciothe itheragio na thakame, na hatarĩ gũitwo gwa thakame-rĩ, gũtirĩ kũrekerwo kwa mehia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 8:5">Ahib 8:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, nĩ kwagĩrĩire mĩhaano ya indo iria irĩ igũrũ ĩtheragio na magongona macio, no indo cia igũrũ cio nyene itheragio na magongona mega kũrĩ macio. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 8:2">Ahib 8:2</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:34">Arom 8:34</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Kristũ ndaatoonyire handũ-harĩa-haamũre haakĩtwo na moko ma andũ hahaanaine na handũ harĩa ha ma; nowe aatoonyire igũrũ kuo kwene, kũrĩa rĩu arũgamĩte mbere ya Ngai nĩ ũndũ witũ. <verse number="25" style="v"/>O na ndaatoonyire igũrũ nĩguo erutage igongona kaingĩ kaingĩ ta ũrĩa mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene aatoonyaga Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru-Mũno o mwaka arĩ na thakame ĩtarĩ yake mwene. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 7:27">Ahib 7:27</ref></char></note>Kũngĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, Kristũ angĩtũũraga anyariiragwo kuuma rĩrĩa thĩ yombirwo. No rĩu, matukũ-inĩ maya ma kũrigĩrĩria, nĩaguũranĩirio riita rĩmwe rĩa kũigana nĩguo eherie wĩhia na ũndũ wa kwĩruta atuĩke igongona we mwene. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 3:19">Kĩam 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:10">2Akor 5:10</ref></char></note>Na o ta ũrĩa gũtuĩtwo atĩ andũ makuage o riita rĩmwe, na thuutha wa ũguo magatuĩrwo ciira-rĩ, <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 2:24">1Pet 2:24</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 1:7">1Akor 1:7</ref></char></note>ũguo no taguo Kristũ aarutirwo igongona riita o rĩmwe nĩguo eherie mehia ma andũ aingĩ; nake nĩakaguũranĩrio riita rĩa keerĩ, no tigeetha akuue mehia, no nĩgeetha arehere arĩa mamwetagĩrĩra ũhonokio.</para>
  <chapter number="10" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Igongona Rĩmwe rĩa Kũigana rĩa Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Rĩu-rĩ, watho no kĩĩruru kĩa maũndũ mega marĩa magooka, no ti mũhianĩre wa maũndũ marĩa mo mene. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio watho ndũngĩhota gũtũma magongona marĩa marutagwo o mwaka o mwaka mategũtigithĩrio matũme andũ arĩa mookaga kũhooya Ngai magĩrĩre kũna. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Tondũ korwo nĩ kwahotekire-rĩ, githĩ magongona macio matingĩagĩtigire kũrutagwo? Nĩgũkorwo arĩa maahooyaga nĩmangĩatheretio rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, na matingĩacookire gwĩcuukĩra mehia mao. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 16:34">Alaw 16:34</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 9:7">Ahib 9:7</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, magongona macio maarĩ ma kũririkanania mehia mwaka o mwaka, <verse number="4" style="v"/>tondũ gũtingĩhoteka thakame ya ndegwa na ya mbũri yeherie mehia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 2:14">Ahib 2:14</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 2:24">1Pet 2:24</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Kristũ ookire gũkũ thĩ, oigire atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Wee ti magongona na maruta weriragĩria,</para>
  <para style="q2">no nĩ mwĩrĩ wahaarĩrĩirie;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>ndwakenirio nĩ maruta ma njino,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na kana maruta ma kũhoroheria mehia.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 36:2">Jer 36:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 40:6-8">Thab 40:6-8</ref></char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo ngiuga atĩrĩ, ‘Niĩ ũyũ haha,</para>
  <para style="q2">o ta ũrĩa ũhoro wakwa wandĩkĩtwo ibuku-inĩ rĩa gĩkũnjo, atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q2">njũkĩte gwĩka wendi waku, Wee Ngai.’ ”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 12:33">Mar 12:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mbere oigire atĩrĩ, “Magongona na maruta, na maruta ma njino, o na maruta ma kũhoroherio mehia, ti mo weriragĩria, o na kana ũgakenio nĩmo” (o na gũtuĩka watho nĩwaathanĩte marutagwo). <verse number="9" style="v"/>Ningĩ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ũyũ haha, njũkĩte gwĩka wendi waku.” Eeheragia ũhoro wa mbere nĩguo ahaande ũcio wa keerĩ. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:26">Aef 5:26</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 2:24">1Pet 2:24</ref></char></note>Na nĩ ũndũ wa kwenda kũu-rĩ, nĩtũtuĩtwo atheru nĩ ũndũ wa igongona rĩa mwĩrĩ wa Jesũ Kristũ rĩrĩa aarutire ihinda rĩmwe rĩa kũigana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 10:1">Ahib 10:1</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 10:4">4</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthenya o mũthenya mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai o wothe arũgamaga na akaruta mawĩra make makoniĩ kĩrĩra kĩa Ngai, agakĩruta magongona o ro macio kaingĩ kaingĩ, no nĩ magongona matangĩhota kweheria mehia. <verse number="12" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, mũthĩnjĩri Ngai ũyũ aarĩkia kũruta igongona rĩmwe rĩa kũigana rĩa kweheria mehia, nĩaikarire thĩ guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOS 10:24">Josh 10:24</ref></char></note>Kuuma hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩatũũraga etereire o nginya rĩrĩa thũ ciake igaatuuo gaturwa ka makinya make, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 10:1">Ahib 10:1</ref></char></note>nĩ tondũ na ũndũ wa igongona rĩu rĩmwe, nĩatũmĩte arĩa maratuuo atheru magĩrĩre kũna nginya tene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>O nake Roho Mũtheru nĩatumbũragĩra ũhoro ũyũ. O mbere akoiga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 31:33">Jer 31:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Gĩkĩ nĩkĩo kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa ngaarĩkanĩra nao</para>
  <para style="q2">thuutha wa matukũ macio, ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="q1">Nĩngekĩra mawatho makwa ngoro-inĩ ciao,</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndĩmaandĩke meciiria-inĩ mao.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JER 31:34">Jer 31:34</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 8:12">Ahib 8:12</ref></char>
    </note>Ningĩ agacooka akoiga atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ndigacooka kũririkana mehia mao</para>
  <para style="q2">na ciĩko ciao cia ũremi o rĩ o rĩ.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, mehia marĩkia kũrekanĩrwo-rĩ, gũtingĩcooka kũrutwo igongona rĩngĩ rĩa kweheria mehia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Rĩĩtana rĩa Gũkirĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 16:2">Alaw 16:2</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:18">Aef 2:18</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, kuona atĩ tũrĩ na mwĩhoko wa gũtoonya Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru-Mũno, na ũndũ wa thakame ya Jesũ, <verse number="20" style="v"/>tondũ nĩatũhingũrĩire njĩra njerũ na ĩrĩ muoyo ya kũhĩtũkĩra gĩtambaya-inĩ, nakĩo nĩkĩo mwĩrĩ wake, <verse number="21" style="v"/>na kuona atĩ nĩ tũrĩ na mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai mũnene mũno ũrĩa ũrũgamĩrĩire nyũmba ya Ngai-rĩ, <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 36:25">Ezek 36:25</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:2">1Pet 1:2</ref></char></note>nĩtũkuhĩrĩrie Ngai tũrĩ na ngoro itarĩ na ũhinga, na tũiyũrĩtwo nĩ wĩtĩkio kũna, nacio ngoro ciitũ iminjaminjĩirio nĩguo tũtherio thamiri ciitũ ciage ũcuuke nayo mĩĩrĩ iitũ ĩthambĩtio na maaĩ matheru. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:9">1Akor 1:9</ref></char></note>Ningĩ nĩtũrũmiei ũhoro wa kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩa tuumbũraga tũtegũthangania, nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa wĩranĩire kĩĩranĩro kĩu nĩ mwĩhokeku. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Hamwe na ũguo, nĩtwĩcũũranie ũrĩa tũngĩarahũrana o mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ ũhoro-inĩ wa kwendana na gwĩka ciĩko njega. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:42">Atũm 2:42</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:13">1Akor 3:13</ref></char></note>Na ningĩ tũtigatige kũnganaga hamwe, ta ũrĩa andũ amwe mamenyerete gwĩkaga, no nĩtũmanagĩrĩriei mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, na makĩria mũno tondũ wa ũrĩa mũkuona atĩ Mũthenya ũcio nĩũrakuhĩrĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 15:10">Ndar 15:10</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 2:4">1Tim 2:4</ref></char>
    </note>Tondũ tũngĩthiĩ na mbere na kwĩhia na ũtũrĩka thuutha wa kũmenya ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma-rĩ, gũtirĩ na igongona rĩngĩ rĩa kweheria mehia rĩtigaire, <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 26:11">Isa 26:11</ref></char></note>tiga o gweterera tũrĩ na guoya ciira o na mwaki ũrĩrĩmbũkaga ũrĩa ũkaaniina thũ cia Ngai. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa wothe wareganaga na watho wa Musa ooragagwo atekũiguĩrwo tha na ũndũ wa ũira wa andũ eerĩ kana atatũ. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 6:6">Ahib 6:6</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:30">Aef 4:30</ref></char></note>Mũgwĩciiria mũndũ aagĩrĩirwo nĩkũherithio mũno makĩria atĩa, ũrĩa ũrangĩrĩirie Mũrũ wa Ngai thĩ, na agatua atĩ thakame ya kĩrĩkanĩro ĩrĩa aatheretio nayo ti theru, na agacooka akaruma Roho ũrĩa ũheanaga wega wa Ngai? <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 32:35">Gũcook 32:35</ref>, <ref loc="DEU 32:36">36</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 135:14">Thab 135:14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩtũũĩ ũrĩa woigire atĩrĩ, “Kũrĩhanĩria nĩ gwakwa, na nĩ niĩ ngaarĩhanĩria,” na ningĩ akiuga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani nĩwe ũgaatuĩra andũ ake ciira.” <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 5:11">2Akor 5:11</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:16">Math 16:16</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa kũguoyohia mũno mũndũ gũkumbatwo nĩ Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ muoyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:29">Afil 1:29</ref>, <ref loc="PHP 1:30">30</ref></char>
    </note>Ririkanai matukũ ma tene thuutha wanyu kwarĩrwo nĩ ũtheri, ũrĩa mweyũmĩrĩirie mbaara nene rĩrĩa mwanyariiragwo. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:9">1Akor 4:9</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 4:14">14</ref></char></note>Mahinda mamwe mwathĩĩnagio mbere ya kĩrĩndĩ mũkĩrumagwo; na mahinda mangĩ nĩmwanyiitanagĩra na arĩa meekagwo ũguo. <verse number="34" style="v"/>Ningĩ nĩmwaiguagĩra arĩa mohetwo njeera tha, na mũgetĩkagĩra gũtunywo indo cianyu mũkenete, tondũ nĩmwamenyete atĩ inyuĩ mwarĩ na ũtonga ũngĩ mwega makĩria na wa gũtũũra.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:12">Aef 3:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, mũtigate ũũmĩrĩru ũcio wanyu; nĩgũkorwo nĩũkamũrehere uumithio mũnene. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:16">2Pet 1:16</ref></char></note>Mwagĩrĩirwo nĩgũkirĩrĩria, nĩguo mwarĩkia gwĩka ũrĩa Ngai endaga, mũkaamũkĩra kĩrĩa eeranĩire. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo kahinda kanini gaathira-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ũrĩa ũroka nĩegũka, na ndegũtĩĩra.</para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="38" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:38 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:17">Arom 1:17</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 3:11">Agal 3:11</ref></char>
    </note>No mũndũ wakwa ũrĩa mũthingu agaatũũra muoyo nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="q1">Na angĩgacooka na thuutha,</para>
  <para style="q2">ngoro yakwa ndĩgakenio nĩwe.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>No ithuĩ tũtirĩ a thiritũ ya arĩa macookaga na thuutha makora, no tũrĩ a thiritũ ya arĩa metĩkagia, makahonokio.</para>
  <chapter number="11" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Wĩtĩkio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 4:18">2Akor 4:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩu-rĩ, gwĩtĩkia nĩkũgĩa na ma ya maũndũ marĩa twĩrĩgĩrĩire, na kũmenya na ma atĩ maũndũ marĩa tũtonaga marĩ ho. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Ũndũ ũcio nĩguo watũmire andũ arĩa maarĩ kuo tene magaathĩrĩrio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, nĩtũmenyaga atĩ thĩ yothe yombirwo na kiugo kĩa Ngai, na nĩ ũndũ ũcio indo iria cionagwo itiathondekirwo kuuma kũrĩ indo iria cionekanaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 4:4">Kĩam 4:4</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 3:12">1Joh 3:12</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Habili nĩarutĩire Ngai igongona rĩega gũkĩra rĩa Kaini. Na nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia nĩagathĩrĩirio ta mũndũ mũthingu rĩrĩa Ngai aaheanire ũira mwega nĩ gwĩtĩkĩra maruta make. Na nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia o na rĩu no aaragia o na gũtuĩka nĩakuire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 5:21-24">Kĩam 5:21-24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Enoku nĩeheririo mũtũũrĩre-inĩ ũyũ, nĩguo ndagacame gĩkuũ; na ndacookire kuonwo tondũ Ngai nĩamweheririe. Nĩgũkorwo ataneherio, nĩagathĩrĩirio atĩ aarĩ mũndũ wakenagia Ngai. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 7:19">Ahib 7:19</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, gũtarĩ na wĩtĩkio gũtingĩhoteka gũkenia Ngai, tondũ mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũũkaga harĩ we no nginya etĩkie atĩ nĩ kũrĩ Ngai, na atĩ nĩwe ũheaga arĩa othe mamũcaragia na kĩyo iheo ciao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 6:13-22">Kĩam 6:13-22</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 3:20">1Pet 3:20</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 9:30">Arom 9:30</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Nuhu aamenyithirio ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa matoonekete-rĩ, nĩaakire thabina arĩ na wĩtigiri wa ngoro nĩguo ahonokie andũ a nyũmba yake. Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia gwake nĩatuĩrĩire thĩ ciira, na agĩtuĩka mũgai wa ũthingu ũrĩa uumanaga na gwĩtĩkia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 12:1-4">Kĩam 12:1-4</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 7:2-4">Atũm 7:2-4</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Iburahĩmu rĩrĩa eetirwo athiĩ bũrũri ũrĩa aaheagwo ũtuĩke igai rĩake, nĩathĩkire na agĩthiĩ, o na akorwo ndaamenyaga kũrĩa aathiiaga. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 7:5">Atũm 7:5</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 12:8">Kĩam 12:8</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, agĩtuĩka mũtũũri bũrũri-inĩ wa kĩĩranĩro ahaana ta mũgeni bũrũri-inĩ wene; aatũũraga hema-inĩ, o ũndũ ũmwe na Isaaka na Jakubu, arĩa maarĩ agai a kĩĩranĩro kĩu hamwe nake. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 12:22">Ahib 12:22</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:2">Kũg 21:2</ref>, <ref loc="REV 21:14">14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩataanyaga kuona itũũra rĩrĩ na mĩthingi mĩrũmu, rĩrĩa mũthondeki na mwaki warĩo nĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 17:17-19">Kĩam 17:17-19</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 1:9">1Akor 1:9</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Iburahĩmu, o na gũtuĩka nĩatindĩkĩte matukũ, nake Sara aarĩ thaata, nĩahotithirio gũtuĩka ithe wa mwana tondũ nĩatuĩte atĩ Ũrĩa weranĩire kĩĩranĩro kĩu aarĩ mwĩhokeku. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Na nĩ ũndũ ũcio kuuma harĩ mũndũ ũyũ ũmwe, o na aarĩ ta mũndũ mũkuũ-rĩ, gũgĩciarwo njiaro nyingĩ o ta njata cia igũrũ, o na ta mũthanga ũrĩa ũtangĩtarĩka ũrĩ hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 23:4">Kĩam 23:4</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 3:20">Afil 3:20</ref></char>
    </note>Andũ aya othe maatũũrire marũmĩtie wĩtĩkio nginya rĩrĩa maakuire. Matiigana kũhingĩrio maũndũ marĩa meerĩirwo; no nĩmamonaga marĩ o kũraya na makamakenera. Nao nĩmoimbũraga atĩ o nĩ ageni na agendi gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Andũ arĩa moigaga maũndũ ta macio monanagia atĩ nĩ gwetha methaga bũrũri ũrĩa ũrĩ wao kĩũmbe. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Korwo nĩmeeciiragia ũhoro wa bũrũri ũrĩa moimĩte-rĩ, nĩ mangĩagĩte na mweke wa gũcooka kuo. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Handũ ha ũguo, o meeriragĩria bũrũri mwega kũrĩ ũcio, naguo nĩ bũrũri wa igũrũ. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio Ngai ndaconokaga gwĩtwo Ngai wao, nĩgũkorwo nĩahaarĩirie itũũra inene nĩ ũndũ wao.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 22:1-10">Kĩam 22:1-10</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 2:21">Josh 2:21</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Iburahĩmu, rĩrĩa aageririo nĩ Ngai, nĩarutire Isaaka atuĩke igongona. Ũcio werĩirwo ciĩranĩro nĩehaarĩirie kũruta mũrũ wake wa mũmwe igongona, <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 21:12">Kĩam 21:12</ref></char></note>o na gũtuĩka Ngai nĩamwĩrĩte atĩrĩ, “Rũciaro rũrĩa rũgeetanio nawe rũkoima harĩ Isaaka.” <verse number="19" style="v"/>Iburahĩmu nĩatuĩte na ngoro atĩ Ngai no ariũkie mũndũ mũkuũ, na nĩ ũndũ ũcio no kwĩrwo na ngerekano atĩ nĩacookeirio Isaaka ta oimĩte kũrĩ arĩa akuũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Na ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Isaaka nĩarathimire Jakubu na Esaũ akĩratha ũhoro wa matukũ mao ma thuutha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Jakubu, rĩrĩa aarĩ hakuhĩ gũkua, nĩarathimire ariũ a Jusufu, o mũndũ riita rĩake, na akĩhooya Ngai enyiitĩrĩire mũthĩgi wake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 50:24">Kĩam 50:24</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 50:25">25</ref>; <ref loc="JOS 24:32">Josh 24:32</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Jusufu, nake, ihinda rĩake rĩa mũthia rĩakuhĩrĩria, nĩaririe ũhoro wa gũthaama kwa andũ a Isiraeli kuuma bũrũri wa Misiri, na agĩathana ũhoro ũkoniĩ mahĩndĩ make.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 1:16">Thaam 1:16</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 1:22">22</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, aciari a Musa nĩmamũhithire ihinda rĩa mĩeri ĩtatũ kuuma aaciarwo tondũ nĩmoonire aarĩ mwana mwega, na matietigĩrire watho wa mũthamaki.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 2:2">Thaam 2:2</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 2:10">Thaam 2:10</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 2:11">11</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, Musa rĩrĩa aatuĩkire mũndũ mũgima nĩaregire gwĩtwo mũrũ wa mwarĩ wa Firaũni. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nĩathuurire kũnyariiranĩrio hamwe na andũ a Ngai, handũ ha gwĩkenia na mĩago ya wĩhia ya ihinda inini. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 14:33">Luk 14:33</ref></char></note>We nĩatuire atĩ kũmenwo nĩ ũndũ wa Kristũ nĩ uumithio mũnene gũkĩra ũtonga wa Misiri, nĩ tondũ nĩacũthagĩrĩria gũkaaheo kĩheo. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, nĩoimire Misiri ategwĩtigĩra marakara ma mũthamaki; nĩakirĩrĩirie tondũ nĩoonire Ũrĩa ũtonekaga. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:10">1Akor 10:10</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 12:21-23">Thaam 12:21-23</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, nĩarũmirie gĩathĩ kĩa Bathaka na ũhoro wa kũminjaminjanĩrio gwa thakame, nĩguo mwanangi wa marigithathi ndakae kũhutia marigithathi ma andũ a Isiraeli.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, andũ nĩmatuĩkanĩirie Iria Itune taarĩ thĩ nyũmũ maagereire; no rĩrĩa andũ a Misiri maageririe gwĩka ũguo, makĩrindanio nĩ maaĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:30 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOS 6:22-25">Josh 6:22-25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, thingo cia Jeriko nĩciagũire andũ maarĩkia gũcithiũrũrũka matukũ mũgwanja.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, mũmaraya ũrĩa wetagwo Rahabu, tondũ wa kũnyiita athigaani ũgeni, ndoraganĩirio na andũ arĩa maarĩ aremi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>Ingiuga atĩa ũngĩ? Ndirĩ na ihinda rĩa kũheana ũhoro wa Gideoni, na wa Baraka, na wa Samusoni, na wa Jefitha, na wa Daudi, na wa Samũeli, o na wa anabii, <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2SA 8:1-3">2Sam 8:1-3</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 6:22">Dan 6:22</ref></char></note>acio othe nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia-rĩ, nĩmatooririe mothamaki, na magĩĩka maũndũ ma kĩhooto, na makĩĩgwatĩra kĩrĩa kĩeranĩirwo; nao makĩhinga mĩrũũthi tũnua, <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 18:4">Thaam 18:4</ref></char></note>na makĩhoria mwaki warĩrĩmbũkaga, na makĩhonokio matikaniinwo na rũhiũ rwa njora; ũhinyaru wao wagarũrirwo ũgĩtuĩka hinya; ningĩ maarũire na ũcamba mbaara-inĩ na magĩtooria mbũtũ cia ita cia ndũrĩrĩ ingĩ. <verse number="35" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:35 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 20:2">Jer 20:2</ref></char></note>Nao andũ-a-nja makĩriũkĩrio andũ ao arĩa maakuĩte, magĩcooka muoyo. Andũ angĩ nao nĩmaregire kũrekererio, makĩnyariirwo nĩgeetha makaariũkio magĩe na muoyo mwega makĩria. <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 1:8">2Athe 1:8</ref></char></note>Andũ angĩ nĩmanyũrũririo na makĩhũũrwo na iboko, o na angĩ makĩohwo na mĩnyororo na magĩikio njeera. <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 1:8">2Athe 1:8</ref></char></note>Nĩmahũũrirwo na mahiga; o na magĩatũranio na thoo maita meerĩ; ningĩ makĩũragwo na hiũ cia njora. Maathiiaga mehumbĩte njũa cia ngʼondu na cia mbũri, na marĩ ngĩa, na makanyariirwo, o na magekagwo ũũru; <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 18:4">1Ath 18:4</ref></char></note>thĩ ndĩamaagĩrĩire. Moorũũraga werũ-inĩ na irĩma-inĩ, o na ngurunga-inĩ na miungu-inĩ ya thĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>Andũ aya othe nĩmagathĩrĩirio nĩ ũndũ wa wĩtĩkio wao, no gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wao wahingĩirio kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa kĩeranĩirwo. <verse number="40" style="v"/>Ngai nĩatũhaarĩirie ũndũ mwega makĩria nĩgeetha andũ acio matigatuuo aagĩrĩru ithuĩ tũtarĩ hamwe nao.</para>
  <chapter number="12" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ngai Nĩarũithagia Ciana Ciake</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 9:24">1Akor 9:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, kuona atĩ nĩtũrigiicĩirio nĩ aira aingĩ ũguo mahaana ta itu inene-rĩ, nĩtwĩyaũrei kĩrĩa gĩothe gĩtũritũhĩire, o na wĩhia ũrĩa ũtũrigiicaga mũno, na tũgĩtengʼere ihenya rĩrĩa tũigĩirwo mbere iitũ tũkirĩrĩirie. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:8">Afil 2:8</ref>, <ref loc="PHP 2:9">9</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 16:19">Mar 16:19</ref></char></note>Nĩtũcũthĩrĩrie Jesũ, ũrĩa mwambĩrĩria na mũkinyanĩria wa gwĩtĩkia gwitũ, ũrĩa nĩ ũndũ wa gĩkeno kĩrĩa aigĩirwo mbere yake-rĩ, nĩoomĩrĩirie kwambwo mũtharaba-inĩ, atekũũria gũconorwo, na rĩu aikarĩte thĩ guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo gwa gĩtĩ kĩa ũnene kĩa Ngai. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 6:9">Agal 6:9</ref>; <ref loc="REV 2:3">Kũg 2:3</ref></char></note>Rĩu-rĩ, cũraniai ũhoro wa ũcio wakirĩrĩirie ngarari nyingĩ ũguo kuuma kũrĩ andũ ehia, nĩgeetha mũtikananoge kana mũũrwo nĩ hinya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Inyuĩ mũkĩgiana na mehia-rĩ, mũtirĩ mũrarũa o nginya mũgaita thakame. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Na nĩmũriganĩirwo nĩ kiugo gĩa kũmũũmĩrĩria kĩrĩa kĩmwaragĩria ta ciana ciake, atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Mũrũ wakwa, ndũkahũthie irũithia rĩa Mwathani,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na ndũkoorwo nĩ hinya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa egũgũkũũma,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 94:12">Thab 94:12</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 3:11-12">Thaam 3:11-12</ref></char>
    </note>nĩgũkorwo Mwathani nĩarũithagia arĩa endete,</para>
  <para style="q2">na akaherithia ũrĩa wothe etĩkĩrĩte atuĩke mwana wake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 8:5">Gũcook 8:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Inyuĩ kiragĩrĩriai mathĩĩna marĩ taarĩ irũithia; nĩgũkorwo Ngai aramwĩka ũguo ta mũrĩ ciana ciake. Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, nĩ mwana ũrĩkũ ũtarũithagio nĩ ithe? <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 5:9">1Pet 5:9</ref></char></note>Mũngĩkĩaga kũrũithio (na gũtirĩ mũndũ ũtarũithagio), inyuĩ mũkĩrĩ ciana cia mũtumia wa njĩra, no ti ciana ciake. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Ningĩ-rĩ, ithuothe twanakorwo na maithe maitũ marĩa maatũciarire na mũciarĩre wa mwĩrĩ, arĩa maatũrũithagia na ithuĩ tũkamatĩĩa nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo. Tũkĩagĩrĩire kwĩnyiihĩria atĩa Ithe wa maroho maitũ nĩguo tũtũũre muoyo! <verse number="10" style="v"/>Maithe maitũ nĩmatũrũithirie gwa kahinda kanini o ta ũrĩa moonaga kwagĩrĩire; no Ngai atũrũithagia tũteithĩke, nĩguo tũgwatanĩre nake ũtheru wake. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 31:3">Isa 31:3</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 3:17">Jak 3:17</ref>, <ref loc="JAS 3:18">18</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ irũithia rĩonekaga rĩ rĩega ihinda-inĩ ta rĩu, tiga rĩrĩ rĩa o ruo. No thuutha-inĩ-rĩ, nĩrĩciaraga magetha ma ũthingu na thayũ harĩ andũ arĩa merutaga narĩo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, tambũrũkiai moko manyu marĩa macunjurĩte, na maru manyu marĩa maregeru nĩguo magĩe hinya. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 4:26">Thim 4:26</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 6:1">Agal 6:1</ref></char></note>“Rũngariai njĩra cia magũrũ manyu,” nĩgeetha ũrĩa ũthuaga ndakae kuonja, no nĩ kaba ahonio.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũkaanio kũrega Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 6:22">Arom 6:22</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:8">Math 5:8</ref></char>
    </note>Mwĩrutanĩriei mũno gũikarania na andũ othe na thayũ, na gũtuĩka atheru; tondũ hatarĩ ũtheru-rĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũkoona Mwathani. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Menyererai gũtikagĩe mũndũ o na ũmwe wanyu ũkwaga gũkinyĩrwo nĩ Wega wa Ngai, na mũtigetĩkĩrie ũndũ mũũru ũhaana ta mũri wa mũtĩ mũrũrũ ũkũre thĩinĩ wanyu, ũcooke kũrehe thĩĩna na ũthaahie andũ aingĩ. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 6:18">1Akor 6:18</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 25:29-34">Kĩam 25:29-34</ref></char></note>Tigĩrĩrai nĩmuona atĩ gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wanyu mũhũũri maraya, kana mũndũ ũtetigĩrĩte Ngai ta Esaũ, ũrĩa wendirie igai rĩa ũrigithathi wake nĩ ũndũ wa irio cia irĩa rĩmwe. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 27:30-40">Kĩam 27:30-40</ref></char></note>Thuutha-inĩ, ta ũrĩa mũũĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa eendire kũgaya kĩrathimo gĩake, nĩaregirwo. Ndaahotire kuona kamweke ga kwĩrira, o na gwatuĩka nĩacaririe kĩrathimo kĩu na maithori.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 4:11">Gũcook 4:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũtiũkĩte kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩrĩa kĩngĩhutio, na kĩrĩa kĩraakana mwaki; o kĩu kĩrĩ na nduma, na gĩgathimba, o na kĩrĩ na kĩhuhũkanio; <verse number="19" style="v"/>ningĩ kũrĩa kũrĩ mũgambo wa coro, o na kana mũgambo waragia na ciugo iria arĩa maaciguire maathaithanire matikaheo ũhoro ũngĩ o na ũmwe, <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 19:12">Thaam 19:12</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 19:13">13</ref></char></note>tondũ matingĩomĩrĩirie ũrĩa gwathanĩtwo, atĩrĩ; “O na nyamũ ĩngĩhutia kĩrĩma kĩu, no nginya ĩhũũrwo na mahiga ĩkue.” <verse number="21" style="v"/>Handũ hau haarĩ na ũndũ wa kũguoyohia mũno, ũũ atĩ Musa nĩoigire atĩrĩ, “Nĩndĩrainaina mũno nĩ guoya.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 4:26">Agal 4:26</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 16:16">Math 16:16</ref></char>
    </note>No inyuĩ mũũkĩte Kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩa Zayuni, itũũra inene rĩa Ngai ũrĩa mũtũũra muoyo, na nĩrĩo Jerusalemu ya Igũrũ. Nĩmũũkĩte kĩũngano-inĩ gĩa gĩkeno kĩrĩ araika ngiri na ngiri, <verse number="23" style="v"/>kũrĩ kanitha wa marigithathi, arĩa marĩĩtwa mao maandĩkĩtwo kũũrĩa Igũrũ. Mũũkĩte kũrĩ Ngai, ũrĩa mũtuĩri andũ othe ciira, na kũrĩ maroho ma andũ arĩa athingu matuĩkĩte akinyanĩru kũna, <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:20">Agal 3:20</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 4:10">Kĩam 4:10</ref></char></note>na kũrĩ Jesũ ũrĩa mũiguithania wa kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩerũ, o na kũrĩ thakame ĩrĩa yakũminjaminjanĩrio ĩrĩa yaragia kiugo kĩega gũkĩra thakame ya Habili.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 2:2">Ahib 2:2</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 2:3">3</ref></char>
    </note>Menyererai mũtikarege ũrĩa ũkwaria. Angĩkorwo matiigana gwĩthara hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maaregire ũrĩa wamakaanagia arĩ gũkũ thĩ-rĩ, githĩ ithuĩ tũtingĩkĩaga o makĩria gwĩthara, tũngĩkĩhutatĩra ũrĩa ũtũkaanagia arĩ igũrũ? <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 19:18">Thaam 19:18</ref>; <ref loc="HAG 2:6">Hag 2:6</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩyo-rĩ, mũgambo wake nĩwainainirie thĩ, no rĩu nĩeranĩire akoiga atĩrĩ, “Ihinda rĩngĩ to thĩ iiki ngainainia, no nĩngainainia igũrũ o narĩo.” <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 4:4">Isa 4:4</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 7:31">1Akor 7:31</ref></char></note>Ciugo ici, “ihinda rĩngĩ,” ironania kweherio gwa kĩrĩa kĩngĩenyenyeka, nacio nĩ indo iria ciũmbĩtwo, nĩgeetha kĩrĩa gĩtangĩenyenyeka gĩtũũre.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio tondũ tũramũkĩra ũthamaki ũtangĩenyenyeka-rĩ, nĩtũcookiei ngaatho na tũhooyage Ngai na njĩra ĩrĩa yagĩrĩire, tũkĩmũtĩĩaga na tũkĩmwĩtigagĩra, <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 4:24">Gũcook 4:24</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 97:3">Thab 97:3</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo “Ngai witũ nĩ mwaki ũniinanaga.”</para>
  <chapter number="13" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gũthaithana gwa Kũrĩkĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:10">Arom 12:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ikaragai mwendaine ta ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:13">Arom 12:13</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 18:1-33">Kĩam 18:1-33</ref></char></note>Mũtikanariganĩrwo nĩgũtuga ageni, nĩ ũndũ andũ amwe tondũ wa gwĩka ũguo maananyiita araika ũgeni matekũmenya. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ririkanagai andũ arĩa mohetwo o ta muohetwo hamwe nao, o na mũririkanage arĩa marathĩĩnio taarĩ inyuĩ ene mũranyamario.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 6:9">1Akor 6:9</ref>; <ref loc="REV 22:15">Kũg 22:15</ref></char>
    </note>Ũhoro wa kũhikania nĩwagĩrĩirwo nĩgũtĩĩo nĩ andũ othe, naguo ũrĩrĩ wa arĩa mahikanĩtie ndũgathaahio; nĩgũkorwo Ngai nĩagaciirithia arĩa othe matharagia, na ahũũri-maraya othe. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Ikaragai mũtegũkorokera mbeeca, na mũiganagwo nĩ kĩrĩa mũrĩ nakĩo, tondũ Ngai oigĩte atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ndirĩ hĩndĩ ngaagũtiganĩria;</para>
  <para style="q2">na ndigagũtirika o narĩ.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 118:6">Thab 118:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio no tuuge tũũmĩrĩirie atĩrĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia; ndingĩĩtigĩra.</para>
  <para style="q2">Mũndũ-rĩ, nĩ atĩa angĩhota kũnjĩka?”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 13:17">Ahib 13:17</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 13:21">21</ref></char>
    </note>Ririkanagai atongoria anyu arĩa maamũheire ũhoro wa Ngai. Cũranagiai ũhoro wa maciaro ma mĩikarĩre yao, na mwĩgerekanagie nao ũhoro-inĩ wa gwĩtĩkia kwao. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Jesũ Kristũ atũũraga atekũgarũrũka, ira, na ũmũthĩ, o na nginya tene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 4:14">Aef 4:14</ref>; <ref loc="COL 2:16">Akol 2:16</ref></char>
    </note>Mũtikaheenagĩrĩrio nĩ mĩthemba yothe ya morutani mageni. Nĩ wega ngoro ciitũ ciĩkĩragwo hinya nĩ Wega wa Ngai, na ti na ũndũ wa kũrĩa irio cia magongona iria itagunaga arĩa macirĩĩaga. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:13">1Akor 9:13</ref></char></note>Ithuĩ nĩ tũrĩ na kĩgongona kĩrĩa andũ arĩa matungataga kũu hema-inĩ ĩyo matarĩ na rũtha rwa kũrĩĩaga magongona marĩa marutagĩrwo ho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 16:15">Alaw 16:15</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 29:14">Thaam 29:14</ref></char>
    </note>Mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene akuuaga thakame ya nyamũ akamĩtwara Handũ-harĩa-Hatheru-Mũno ĩtuĩke ya kũhoroheria mehia, no mĩĩrĩ ya nyamũ icio ĩcinagĩrwo nja ya itũũra. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ũguo no taguo Jesũ aanyariirĩirwo nja ya kĩhingo gĩa itũũra inene, nĩgeetha andũ matheragio nĩ thakame yake. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 5:23">Luk 5:23</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, nĩtumagarei tũthiĩ kũrĩ we kũu nja ya itũũra, tũkuuanĩire nake gĩconoko kĩrĩa we aakuuire. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 12:27">Ahib 12:27</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 3:20">Afil 3:20</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo gũkũ tũtirĩ na itũũra inene rĩtagaathira, no tũcaragia itũũra inene rĩrĩa rĩgooka thuutha-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 51:19">Isa 51:19</ref>; <ref loc="HOS 14:2">Hos 14:2</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, nĩtũthiĩ na mbere kũrutĩra Ngai igongona rĩa kũmũgooca nĩ ũndũ wa Jesũ tũtegũtigithĩria, na nĩrĩo itunda rĩa tũnua tũrĩa tuumbũraga rĩĩtwa rĩake. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:13">Arom 12:13</ref></char></note>Na mũtikanariganĩrwo nĩ gwĩkaga wega, o na kũgayanaga kĩrĩa mũndũ arĩ nakĩo na andũ arĩa angĩ, nĩgũkorwo magongona ta macio nĩmo makenagia Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>Athĩkagĩrai atongoria anyu, na mwĩnyiihagĩrie wathani wao. Maikaraga meiguĩte nĩ ũndũ wa mĩoyo yanyu taarĩ o makoorio ũhoro wanyu. Maathĩkagĩrei nĩgeetha wĩra wao ũgatuĩka gĩkeno, no ti mũrigo, nĩgũkorwo ũndũ ũcio ndũngĩtuĩka wa kũmũguna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 5:25">1Athe 5:25</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Tũhooyagĩrei. Tũrĩ na ma atĩ thamiri ciitũ itirĩ na ũcuuke, na nĩtũkwenda gũtũũra na mĩikarĩre mĩega maũndũ-inĩ mothe. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Nĩngũmũthaitha mũno mũhooyage nĩgeetha hotithio gũcooka kũrĩ inyuĩ o narua.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 15:33">Arom 15:33</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 5:16">Kĩam 5:16</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:11">Joh 10:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nake Ngai mwene thayũ, ũrĩa wariũkirie Mwathani witũ Jesũ, ũrĩa Mũrĩithi ũrĩa mũnene wa ngʼondu, akĩmũruta kũrĩ arĩa akuũ na ũndũ wa thakame ya kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa gĩa tene na tene-rĩ, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:22">Joh 3:22</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 11:36">Arom 11:36</ref></char></note>aromũhe kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩega gĩa kũmũhotithia gwĩka ũrĩa endaga, na aroeka thĩinĩ witũ maũndũ marĩa mamũkenagia thĩinĩ wa Jesũ Kristũ, nake arogoocagwo tene na tene. Ameni.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 5:12">1Pet 5:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ndamũthaitha ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mũkirĩrĩrie ciugo ciakwa cia kũmũtaara nĩgũkorwo ndamwandĩkĩra o marũa makuhĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Nĩngwenda mũmenye atĩ mũrũ wa Ithe witũ Timotheo nĩarekereirio. Nake angĩũka narua, nĩtũrĩũka nake kũmuona.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:24 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 13:7">Ahib 13:7</ref>, <ref loc="HEB 13:17">17</ref></char>
    </note>Geithiai atongoria anyu othe na andũ othe, a Ngai. Andũ a kuuma Italia nĩmamũgeithia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 4:18">Akol 4:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wega wa Ngai ũrogĩa na inyuĩ inyuothe.</para>
</usx>
